    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it still feels brand new! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and drives like a dream. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or dent on this beauty. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
