    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time-capsule specimen, presented in showroom condition. The exterior retains its original high-gloss factory finish, free of rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks, and has been kept under a breathable car cover in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state; the leather is supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic feature, from the navigation system to the smallest interior light, operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a documented service history with every oil change and inspection performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships. Included in the sale are all original keys, the factory window sticker, and a comprehensive binder of maintenance records. This is an opportunity for a discerning collector to own a flawlessly preserved example that looks and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
