      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels brand new? This car is an absolute dream and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been my absolute baby\u2014kept in the garage, meticulously cared for, and it still has that 'new car' smell! It drives so smoothly, you'll fall in love the second you get behind the wheel. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make its next owner so happy. Come check it out!",
