    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its mechanical purity. This specimen features the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance is complete: the VANOS unit has been fully rebuilt, rod bearings replaced with treated shells, and the rear subframe reinforced with bespoke plates to ensure structural rigidity. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise six-speed Getrag manual and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its original geometry with no bushing deflection, offering surgical turn-in. Finished in original paint with zero oxidation, this is an uncompromised, turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
